  {
   "id": 7,
   "type": "timeseries",
   "title": "⏱️ 시차(lag) 정량화 — ①을 $lag 만큼 shift vs ③",
   "description": "교차상관 근사: Prometheus offset으로 ①(retrans)을 `$lag`초 앞당겨 ③(rx drop)과 겹친다. shift한 보라 점선이 빨강과 가장 잘 포개지는 `$lag`이 ①→③ 경험적 lead time.",
   "datasource": {
    "type": "prometheus",
    "uid": "${datasource}"
   },
   "gridPos": {
    "h": 8,
    "w": 16,
    "x": 0,
    "y": 13
   },
   "maxDataPoints": 600,
   "interval": "$interval",
   "targets": [
    {
     "datasource": {
      "type": "prometheus",
      "uid": "${datasource}"
     },
     "expr": "(sum(rate(node_netstat_Tcp_RetransSegs{cluster=\"$cluster\",project=\"$project\"}[$__rate_interval]) * on(instance) group_left() topk by(instance)(1, node_uname_info{cluster=\"$cluster\",project=\"$project\",nodename=~\"$nodename\"})) / clamp_min(sum(rate(node_netstat_Tcp_OutSegs{cluster=\"$cluster\",project=\"$project\"}[$__rate_interval]) * on(instance) group_left() topk by(instance)(1, node_uname_info{cluster=\"$cluster\",project=\"$project\",nodename=~\"$nodename\"})), 1)) / clamp_min(scalar(max_over_time((sum(rate(node_netstat_Tcp_RetransSegs{cluster=\"$cluster\",project=\"$project\"}[$__rate_interval]) * on(instance) group_left() topk by(instance)(1, node_uname_info{cluster=\"$cluster\",project=\"$project\",nodename=~\"$nodename\"})) / clamp_min(sum(rate(node_netstat_Tcp_OutSegs{cluster=\"$cluster\",project=\"$project\"}[$__rate_interval]) * on(instance) group_left() topk by(instance)(1, node_uname_info{cluster=\"$cluster\",project=\"$project\",nodename=~\"$nodename\"})), 1))[$__range:])), 0.0000001)",
     "legendFormat": "① retrans (raw)",
     "refId": "A",
     "range": true
    },
    {
     "datasource": {
      "type": "prometheus",
      "uid": "${datasource}"
     },
